Pre-requisites
--------------

ldns 1.5.0 or later
	http://www.nlnetlabs.nl/projects/ldns/

libevent 2.0.0 or later
	http://monkey.org/~provos/libevent/

Building
--------

If building from SVN:

$ autoreconf --install

then:

$ ./configure --with-ldns=<path-to-ldns> --with-libevent=<path-to-libevent>
# Mac OS X with libraries installed with brew:
# LDFLAGS=-L/usr/local/opt/openssl/lib CPPFLAGS=-I/usr/local/opt/openssl/include ./configure --with-ldns=/usr/local --with-libevent=/usr/local
$ make
